---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        <br />
        Tech Stack:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Java</li>
        <li>C</li>
        <li>Javascript</li>
        <li>SQL</li>
        <li>Power BI</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      I enjoy learning about and using new technologies as well as digging under their layers of abstraction.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Choosing the right tools for the job is essential for building efficient and effective systems.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
